    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Drowned sea-wolves risen as undead. Fur matted with slime and ice, eyes white and sightless. Hunt by sound and smell in the flooded cave system beneath Svellheim.</p>",
      "director": "<p><strong>ABILITIES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Bite</strong> (Main, Melee, Might): T1 2 dmg; T2 5 dmg; T3 7 dmg.</li><li><strong>Frenzy Snap</strong> (Main, Close burst 2, Might): T1 3 dmg; T2 6 dmg + target vulnerable EoNT; T3 8 dmg + vulnerable (save ends).</li></ul><p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Blind Sense:</strong> Immune to visibility effects. Senses by sound/scent. Stealth vs these wolves requires complete silence.</li><li><strong>Aquatic Advantage:</strong> Speed 8 in water. Melee attacks against it in water: −1 penalty.</li></ul><p>Pack of 6. Beat 11 Bioluminescent Grotto. Combined with 1 Dire Draugr Wolf.</p>",
